{"tid":1157143,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"霸氣司機拒讓步　企硬頂死逆線車　網民狂呼爽！","createTime":"2019-05-16T05:21:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-16T05:29:41.000Z","uid":225464,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"12836afca4c30b4d9bd936b136a003f7ca4fa900","tid":1157143,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T05:21:51.000Z","msg":"霸氣司機拒讓步 企硬頂死逆線車 網民狂呼爽！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2W3jdWJ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2W3jdWJ&d=nKoZ4xrs0zkQ%2F022jTHdf2t2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=deb5c785\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2W3jdWJ</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190516/photo/bkn-20190516123813905-0516_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190516131818\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190516%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190516123813905-0516_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190516131818&h=afcc58ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n逆線仲想人讓？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網民Ck Leung在Facebook群組「小心駕駛（討論別人駕駛態度）」上傳影片，據畫面所示，周二（14日）上午8時許，他正駕車準備駛入朗屏邨屏義路。當時出口處有不少車輛正排隊等候轉出。<br />\n<br />\n有私家車疑不想排隊，逆線「打尖」，未料在出口處卻「巧遇」片主。片主未有讓步，更頂住私家車慢慢前駛，迫使私家車倒車。他怒斥︰「大把老X奉慣犯，架車仲要等我過咗，就大油繼續逆線」。"},{"pid":"38cebf3d07731e8c8aec9dfe29ba2cf10c32f95d","tid":1157143,"uid":196751,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T05:26:14.000Z","msg":"仆街太多,有骨氣既人太少"},{"pid":"05cd42e62c9204f521c4dbae27238f58234ad1f4","tid":1157143,"uid":120715,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T05:27:07.000Z","msg":"順便交埋段片俾警察啦"},{"pid":"031435a56617b028f277f30a8bb12ae124a2aa47","tid":1157143,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"38cebf3d07731e8c8aec9dfe29ba2cf10c32f95d","tid":1157143,"uid":196751,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T05:26:14.000Z","msg":"仆街太多,有骨氣既人太少"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T05:29:41.000Z","msg":"啱呀<br />\n上次有呂屍機居然讓畀逆線L行"}]}